high_descs: Turn around and go straight and to the left to get to the sofa.
Pick up the knife from the sofa.
Go left and right to go around the sofa into the pathway, then left to the bathroom.
Slice the loaf of bread inside the sink.
Exit the room the way you came in, turn right and then right again at the table, stopping at the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Return to the bathroom with the bread.
Pick up one slice of bread.
Go back to the table with the microwave and keep walking straight, stopping at the fridge on the left.
Place the bread slice in the fridge, let it cool, then remove it.
Go back to the microwave.
Place the bread slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled slice of bread in a microwave.
